Addressed the cleanup comments
This has been submited as a [PR](https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/341) for BIP 133.

@paveljanik It's impossible to be sure there aren't invs or txs in flight with fee rates below the cut off. Also in general we don't have a good system for responding to p2p misbehavior.  I think this could be extended later with that ability, but as of now it does not appear
